Places to Visit in Jodhpur

Mehrangarh Fort is perhaps the most celebrated of places to visit in Jodhpur but there are so many other irresistible Jodhpur tourist places too some visitors end up adding days to their itinerary. Just some examples are Kheechan Bird Sanctuary, Umaid Bhawan Palace, Udai Mandir, and Jaswant Thada. Check out this page for a sneak peek into other wonderful Jodhpur places to visit.
